WEBVTT

01:42.940 --> 01:46.090
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:49.030
[Episode 1]

01:58.750 --> 02:00.350
Jiang Chengyi, look over here.

02:03.190 --> 02:04.310
What are you recording?

02:06.630 --> 02:07.510
Recording us.

02:15.790 --> 02:16.910
Hello, Anesthesiology Department.

02:17.550 --> 02:18.430
The Emergency Department just sent over

02:18.430 --> 02:19.720
a patient with acute gastric hemorrhage.

02:19.790 --> 02:20.630
He needs surgery immediately.

02:20.790 --> 02:21.430
I'll be right there.

02:24.290 --> 02:25.170
[Exit]

02:31.910 --> 02:32.829
[Arterial transducer]

02:32.900 --> 02:33.829
[Spinal anesthesia kit]

02:52.829 --> 02:53.600
Dr. Lu.

02:53.620 --> 02:54.470
The general surgery ward requires

02:54.470 --> 02:55.910
a central venous catheterization.

02:59.990 --> 03:00.780
Okay, got it.

03:02.620 --> 03:03.330
There's an Emergency Department patient

03:03.360 --> 03:04.520
suffering from a ruptured aortic dissection.

03:04.540 --> 03:05.530
They require intubation

03:05.660 --> 03:06.630
and deep anesthesia.

03:07.190 --> 03:07.950
I'll be right there.

03:07.860 --> 03:09.180
[Emergency Department]

03:17.950 --> 03:19.550
I'm going to administer the epidural now.

03:19.840 --> 03:21.320
If you experience contractions later,

03:21.350 --> 03:22.220
tell me immediately.

03:22.270 --> 03:23.270
I'll stop right away.

03:23.310 --> 03:23.950
Alright?

03:24.750 --> 03:25.430
Doctor.

03:25.829 --> 03:26.670
Will this epidural

03:26.670 --> 03:28.400
affect the child in any way?

03:29.750 --> 03:30.700
Don't worry.

03:30.910 --> 03:32.540
Our dosage is very low.

03:32.710 --> 03:33.670
Just stay still.

03:34.030 --> 03:34.630
Okay?

03:40.820 --> 03:43.910
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

03:46.950 --> 03:47.829
Dr. Han.

03:48.680 --> 03:50.090
Chengyi just came back.

03:50.990 --> 03:52.270
I have to trouble you

03:52.510 --> 03:53.470
to introduce

03:53.510 --> 03:54.750
his father's condition once again.

03:55.110 --> 03:55.829
Also,

03:56.510 --> 03:57.960
you advised us last time

03:58.390 --> 03:59.920
that Jiang should have the surgery.

04:00.710 --> 04:02.140
We just want to ask whether

04:02.510 --> 04:04.350
it's possible to continue with conservative treatment.

04:05.270 --> 04:06.030
Five years ago,

04:06.030 --> 04:07.630
Jiang found out about the thymic tumor.

04:08.190 --> 04:08.990
As it was benign,

04:09.070 --> 04:10.430
we've been managing it with medication.

04:10.830 --> 04:11.710
There was no issue.

04:12.790 --> 04:14.260
But take a look now.

04:15.650 --> 04:16.529
The tumor

04:17.029 --> 04:17.950
is growing.

04:19.190 --> 04:20.269
It looks normal on the surface,

04:20.750 --> 04:21.940
but it is growing towards

04:22.029 --> 04:23.460
the back of the sternum.

04:24.390 --> 04:25.500
There are already signs that

04:25.630 --> 04:27.260
it is oppressing the trachea.

04:28.910 --> 04:30.270
As his primary care doctor,

04:30.990 --> 04:31.670
I'd recommend

04:32.470 --> 04:33.540
surgery as soon as possible.

04:35.990 --> 04:36.500
Then...

04:39.030 --> 04:39.870
Dr. Han,

04:40.470 --> 04:41.270
can't we...

04:42.510 --> 04:44.280
manage it with drugs now?

04:44.350 --> 04:45.750
It is possible.

04:45.990 --> 04:46.580
But...

04:47.140 --> 04:49.390
This is a ticking time bomb.

04:52.830 --> 04:53.510
Right now,

04:53.909 --> 04:55.790
it is the best time for surgery.

04:59.230 --> 04:59.750
Come in.

05:03.030 --> 05:03.630
Dr. Han.

05:04.590 --> 05:05.360
This is

05:05.390 --> 05:06.810
the anesthesiologist for our surgery.

05:07.310 --> 05:08.110
Lu Yan, Dr. Lu.

05:10.030 --> 05:10.710
Hello, Auntie.

05:11.870 --> 05:13.020
Hello, Dr. Lu.

05:13.870 --> 05:14.830
Dr. Lu,

05:15.790 --> 05:17.030
you're so young.

05:23.370 --> 05:25.310
This is my son, Jiang Chengyi.

05:39.140 --> 05:39.730
Hello.

05:41.670 --> 05:42.230
Hello.

05:48.710 --> 05:49.870
Dr. Lu.

05:50.190 --> 05:51.190
Do you think

05:52.390 --> 05:52.950
my husband

05:52.950 --> 05:54.450
can handle the anesthesia?

05:55.230 --> 05:56.420
Dr. Han previously showed me

05:56.450 --> 05:58.090
the patient's full medical records.

05:58.350 --> 05:59.440
The patient's physical condition

05:59.470 --> 06:00.270
can endure both

06:00.270 --> 06:01.620
surgery and anesthesia.

06:01.830 --> 06:03.050
That is why we suggest

06:03.140 --> 06:04.240
it is best to remove

06:04.270 --> 06:05.660
the tumor as soon as possible.

06:06.750 --> 06:07.340
Dr. Lu,

06:07.910 --> 06:09.280
tell them more about your anesthesia plan.

06:10.670 --> 06:11.790
After a comprehensive assessment,

06:11.830 --> 06:12.990
I suggest general anesthesia

06:13.020 --> 06:14.550
and intubation.

06:15.830 --> 06:16.710
General anesthesia?

06:17.470 --> 06:18.760
And even intubation?

06:18.830 --> 06:19.440
Auntie,

06:19.470 --> 06:20.560
it might sound scary,

06:20.590 --> 06:21.620
but it's actually not that scary.

06:21.950 --> 06:22.550
Let me give you...

06:22.670 --> 06:23.590
I don't agree to the surgery.

06:27.930 --> 06:28.670
Mom, take a seat.

06:32.909 --> 06:33.620
It's great that

06:34.170 --> 06:35.230
Dr. Han is here,

06:36.140 --> 06:37.260
and so is the anesthesiologist.

06:38.070 --> 06:39.150
I would like to ask

06:39.980 --> 06:40.950
for someone like my father,

06:40.980 --> 06:42.190
who has severe sick sinus syndrome

06:42.860 --> 06:44.670
and history of cerebral hemorrhage,

06:45.880 --> 06:47.900
what is the risk of anesthesia and surgery?

06:50.070 --> 06:51.610
There is indeed a risk.

06:51.790 --> 06:53.870
But sick sinus syndrome and cerebral hemorrhage are not

06:53.990 --> 06:54.960
absolute contraindications

06:54.990 --> 06:56.550
for surgery and anesthesia.

06:56.710 --> 06:57.350
We can only conclude

06:57.390 --> 06:58.590
that compared to other patients,

06:58.620 --> 07:00.030
the risk is higher for this surgery.

07:00.170 --> 07:00.730
Yes.

07:01.190 --> 07:02.260
In other words,

07:02.390 --> 07:04.210
while being under anesthesia,

07:04.390 --> 07:05.870
his blood pressure may fluctuate

07:06.510 --> 07:08.350
and cause cerebral hemorrhage.

07:09.550 --> 07:10.470
This will affect his life,

07:10.470 --> 07:10.870
right?

07:13.670 --> 07:14.300
Yes.

07:14.870 --> 07:16.230
But I am fully aware of

07:16.260 --> 07:17.110
his past medical history.

07:17.130 --> 07:17.920
So I will be very careful

07:17.950 --> 07:19.110
when it comes to this operation.

07:20.390 --> 07:21.160
Even so,

07:22.280 --> 07:23.520
the risk still exists.

07:25.940 --> 07:27.390
But every operation...

07:27.620 --> 07:28.670
has its own risks.

07:28.670 --> 07:29.190
Dr. Han,

07:30.800 --> 07:31.790
you've already explained

07:31.790 --> 07:32.860
very clearly to me.

07:33.350 --> 07:34.250
I want to know

07:34.310 --> 07:35.790
if we still continue with

07:35.820 --> 07:36.909
conservative treatment,

07:38.110 --> 07:39.070
is there a possibility

07:39.070 --> 07:39.670
for the tumor to grow?

07:41.550 --> 07:42.100
No.

07:42.900 --> 07:43.960
A benign tumor

07:44.030 --> 07:45.510
usually won't grow rapidly.

07:45.909 --> 07:46.880
But...

07:47.110 --> 07:48.390
The location of this tumor

07:48.520 --> 07:49.520
is very unusual.

07:49.909 --> 07:51.020
It could potentially cause

07:51.150 --> 07:52.230
hazardous situations.

07:52.570 --> 08:01.110
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

07:53.190 --> 07:54.830
If that's the case,

07:55.630 --> 07:56.750
I still hope my father

07:56.830 --> 07:58.710
can continue with conservative treatment.

07:59.860 --> 08:01.250
Unless absolutely necessary,

08:03.550 --> 08:04.990
I don’t want him to take the risk.

08:11.940 --> 08:12.690
Jiang.

08:13.620 --> 08:14.690
Are you worried about

08:15.070 --> 08:16.380
Dr. Lu's abilities?

08:17.590 --> 08:19.250
She is my best student.

08:19.630 --> 08:20.900
Her major in university

08:21.070 --> 08:22.190
was anesthesiology.

08:22.670 --> 08:24.180
Before becoming the lead anesthesiologist,

08:24.400 --> 08:26.170
she had already been a junior anesthesiologist for three years.

08:26.670 --> 08:28.990
She had been a part of thousands of surgeries.

08:30.110 --> 08:32.710
Ever since she became lead anesthesiologist,

08:33.190 --> 08:34.840
Dr. Lu has personally been in-charge of

08:35.230 --> 08:36.720
over 400 operations.

08:36.870 --> 08:37.750
There has never been

08:37.789 --> 08:38.510
any accident.

08:38.780 --> 08:42.419
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

08:38.990 --> 08:39.720
Dr. Han.

08:40.390 --> 08:40.990
I'm not doubting

08:40.990 --> 08:42.260
the competence of your hospital's doctors.

08:42.990 --> 08:44.140
I just don't want my father

08:44.140 --> 08:44.830
to take the risk.

08:48.870 --> 08:49.380
Dr. Han,

08:51.250 --> 08:52.860
I respect the family's wishes.

08:58.150 --> 08:59.390
Dr. Lu, I...

08:59.390 --> 09:00.710
Auntie, it's okay.

09:01.310 --> 09:02.270
A surgery

09:02.310 --> 09:03.840
requires not only the doctors' efforts

09:03.870 --> 09:05.140
and the patient's cooperation,

09:05.470 --> 09:06.930
but more importantly, we need

09:12.230 --> 09:13.390
mutual support and trust.

09:15.790 --> 09:16.430
Dr. Lu,

09:18.150 --> 09:19.430
send the patient's family back.

09:19.950 --> 09:20.430
I...

09:21.590 --> 09:22.430
Why hesitate?

09:23.320 --> 09:23.920
On the way,

09:23.950 --> 09:25.470
have a good chat with the family

09:26.350 --> 09:27.450
and persuade them

09:28.110 --> 09:29.230
to agree to the surgery.

09:29.500 --> 09:30.470
As you know,

09:30.550 --> 09:31.540
the patient's condition is complicated.

09:31.620 --> 09:32.430
The more we hesitate,

09:32.550 --> 09:33.430
the more dangerous it becomes.

09:35.020 --> 09:35.740
Dr. Han...

09:36.110 --> 09:37.180
I've got a few things to do.

09:37.540 --> 09:38.350
I have asked Dr. Lu

09:38.380 --> 09:39.540
to walk you back to the ward.

09:39.990 --> 09:40.430
Okay.

09:40.470 --> 09:41.250
Thank you.

09:42.070 --> 09:42.730
I'm leaving.

09:45.190 --> 09:46.140
This way, Auntie.

09:46.190 --> 09:46.630
Okay.

09:46.660 --> 09:47.830
Sorry for the trouble, Dr. Lu.

09:47.910 --> 09:48.390
It's okay.

10:08.480 --> 10:09.260
Hold on a second!

10:09.900 --> 10:11.110
Hold on, please.

10:40.550 --> 10:42.260
This is the first floor.

10:50.870 --> 10:51.670
Dr. Lu.

10:51.670 --> 10:53.350
We know how to get to the ward.

10:53.410 --> 10:54.310
There's no need to come along.

11:04.590 --> 11:05.230
Jiang Chengyi.

11:05.190 --> 11:09.440
[Department of Ultrasound Medicine] [Outpatient Pharmacy]

11:07.890 --> 11:08.460
What?

11:09.950 --> 11:11.060
If you have a problem with me,

11:11.080 --> 11:12.380
you can change the anesthesiologist.

11:12.790 --> 11:13.510
But I sincerely suggest

11:13.530 --> 11:14.590
to do the surgery as soon as possible.

11:15.410 --> 11:18.150
♫To meet you in this big world♫

11:15.870 --> 11:17.680
I personally have no problem with you.

11:18.150 --> 11:19.350
Don’t read too much into it.

11:18.860 --> 11:21.290
♫I'm excited like a child♫

11:19.990 --> 11:20.500
Dr. Lu.

11:22.190 --> 11:23.230
You are not that important to me.

11:22.270 --> 11:28.070
♫As we carve our future♫

11:29.240 --> 11:31.840
♫You're like the day that breaks up the night♫

11:32.760 --> 11:35.240
♫You gave no reason as you turned around and left♫

11:33.250 --> 11:34.900
[Department of Ultrasound Medicine] [Outpatient Pharmacy]

11:36.390 --> 11:40.610
♫Like smoke that drifts away♫

11:41.760 --> 11:43.660
♫I don't understand♫

11:45.010 --> 11:46.700
♫How can I understand?♫

11:48.940 --> 11:53.430
♫You don't exist♫

11:55.150 --> 12:00.570
♫Our love still exists♫

12:01.480 --> 12:07.420
♫It's impossible to be apart♫

12:08.230 --> 12:08.850
Lu Yan

12:10.210 --> 12:15.350
♫Our love still exists♫

12:10.870 --> 12:11.430
Lu Yan.

12:14.910 --> 12:15.670
Why do you want to break up?

12:16.680 --> 12:22.160
♫I want to hear you telling the truth♫

12:23.350 --> 12:25.960
♫You know me best♫

12:24.350 --> 12:25.060
We...

12:26.030 --> 12:26.780
are not suitable

12:27.100 --> 12:30.140
♫If we just struggled a bit♫

12:31.050 --> 12:38.480
♫We'll overcome despair♫

12:43.310 --> 12:44.350
This tumor of mine

12:44.370 --> 12:46.590
is a benign one.

12:47.830 --> 12:50.240
It's not the first time we've discovered it.

12:50.900 --> 12:53.220
Why did you have to fly back?

12:54.700 --> 12:55.940
What about the cases

12:55.990 --> 12:56.710
on your hand?

12:57.700 --> 13:01.710
[Bed 3]

12:57.950 --> 12:59.380
You're being irresponsible

12:59.430 --> 13:00.780
with your job.

13:01.810 --> 13:04.150
You are disregarding the organisation

13:04.540 --> 13:05.610
and lack discipline.

13:05.820 --> 13:06.270
All right.

13:06.310 --> 13:07.700
The doctor asked you to talk less.

13:07.720 --> 13:08.550
Here, drink some water.

13:17.160 --> 13:18.690
What did Dr. Han say?

13:22.830 --> 13:24.340
Dr. Han said you're fine.

13:24.790 --> 13:25.870
The tumor is benign.

13:24.860 --> 13:26.120
[Bed 3]

13:26.070 --> 13:27.020
But look at you!

13:27.700 --> 13:28.990
Ever since you heard that your son is coming back,

13:29.270 --> 13:29.750
how many times

13:29.750 --> 13:30.910
have you secretly sneaked a smile?

13:32.590 --> 13:34.350
But, you scold him as soon as he comes back.

13:34.670 --> 13:35.550
Why are you being like this?

13:35.550 --> 13:36.390
Right, Chengyi?

13:37.950 --> 13:38.310
Yes.

13:38.330 --> 13:39.230
Alright.

13:39.990 --> 13:41.340
Let's talk about you.

13:42.420 --> 13:44.470
I've just been hospitalized for a few days,

13:44.590 --> 13:45.710
but you have added all of

13:45.730 --> 13:47.350
the hospital's single female doctors

13:48.060 --> 13:49.330
and female nurses

13:49.390 --> 13:50.470
as contacts on WeChat, right?

13:51.250 --> 13:51.940
You've discovered?

13:52.670 --> 13:53.330
Aren't I something?

13:53.470 --> 13:54.110
Yes, indeed.

13:54.920 --> 13:55.990
Let me tell you.

13:56.230 --> 13:57.710
Today, I met...

13:58.030 --> 13:59.070
Dr. Lu.

13:59.240 --> 14:00.630
She's a nice person.

14:00.790 --> 14:01.650
Eight-year program,

14:01.790 --> 14:02.620
anesthesiology department.

14:02.650 --> 14:04.410
An outstanding student in the integrated bachelor's and master's program.

14:05.070 --> 14:07.100
She's gentle and clear,

14:07.350 --> 14:08.310
with high EQ.

14:09.270 --> 14:10.030
In the future,

14:10.110 --> 14:12.140
there’s absolutely no need to worry about conflicts between us as in-laws.

14:12.900 --> 14:14.690
Mom, what are you thinking?

14:17.520 --> 14:18.270
The point is...

14:18.710 --> 14:20.260
she's pretty.

14:22.070 --> 14:22.980
Enough.

14:23.010 --> 14:24.730
Say no more.

14:25.130 --> 14:26.880
They will be miles apart.

14:27.110 --> 14:28.900
Chengyi hasn’t been transferred back yet.

14:29.060 --> 14:29.700
It won't last.

14:30.390 --> 14:31.750
Why would it be?

14:32.480 --> 14:34.100
Just ask Chengyi to come back.

14:34.190 --> 14:35.510
Don’t you want him to come back too?

14:35.590 --> 14:36.110
Mom.

14:36.140 --> 14:37.570
We can’t just request a transfer whenever we want

14:37.630 --> 14:38.870
That's for normal units.

14:39.830 --> 14:40.350
I don't care.

14:41.860 --> 14:43.230
You are busy with work every day.

14:43.980 --> 14:45.710
I haven't seen you smile even in the past few days.

14:46.300 --> 14:47.230
Maybe...

14:47.510 --> 14:48.350
Maybe it will be better

14:48.370 --> 14:49.310
once you have a girlfriend.

14:49.550 --> 14:50.790
What does it have to do with that?

14:51.230 --> 14:52.270
When I see the both of you,

14:52.300 --> 14:52.750
don't I

14:52.990 --> 14:53.950
smile rather happily?

14:53.970 --> 14:54.500
Right, Dad?

14:55.940 --> 14:57.420
You look worse than when you cry.

14:59.100 --> 14:59.680
Enough.

14:59.830 --> 15:00.870
Pass this apple to him.

15:05.370 --> 15:05.860
No...

15:06.260 --> 15:06.960
You eat.

15:06.980 --> 15:07.740
It's okay.

15:07.790 --> 15:08.350
You meant that for him?

15:08.380 --> 15:09.330
-It’s okay.
-I’ll peel another one.

15:09.470 --> 15:10.070
No, no.

15:10.110 --> 15:10.990
Let's share one.

15:10.990 --> 15:11.410
Here.

15:11.790 --> 15:12.440
Be good.

15:13.420 --> 15:14.310
That's great.

15:15.390 --> 15:15.870
Is it sweet?

15:15.920 --> 15:16.620
Yes.

15:17.170 --> 15:18.660
It's sweet because our son peeled it.

15:21.750 --> 15:23.730
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

15:33.110 --> 15:33.860
Dr. Lu.

15:33.990 --> 15:34.600
You're off work?

15:34.790 --> 15:35.270
I'm leaving.

15:35.590 --> 15:36.450
Goodbye.

15:36.910 --> 15:38.390
♫As the city flickers♫

15:39.610 --> 15:42.390
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

15:43.670 --> 15:45.100
♫And you, who love to smile♫

15:45.980 --> 15:48.660
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

15:49.470 --> 15:51.810
♫The humor of time♫

15:53.300 --> 15:55.750
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

15:56.820 --> 16:02.570
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

16:03.960 --> 16:05.570
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

16:06.690 --> 16:09.540
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

16:10.830 --> 16:12.330
♫The stubborn me♫

16:13.490 --> 16:16.190
♫I always think of the far future♫

16:16.980 --> 16:19.050
♫I walk willfully♫

16:19.670 --> 16:20.350
Dr. Lu!

16:20.420 --> 16:23.340
♫Like a star revolving around♫

16:20.630 --> 16:21.070
Dr. Lu.

16:21.150 --> 16:22.340
Do you still want the pomelo you ordered?

16:23.980 --> 16:25.290
♫I turn around♫

16:26.460 --> 16:30.090
♫But you're not behind me♫

16:31.620 --> 16:33.210
♫Losing you♫

16:34.030 --> 16:36.390
♫It's so unreal♫

16:37.400 --> 16:38.960
♫I hurt my love♫

16:39.540 --> 16:40.490
♫But still hope to♫

16:41.230 --> 16:43.930
♫Start anew♫

16:43.570 --> 16:49.410
[Huiting Complex]

16:45.130 --> 16:47.280
♫There’s a certain kind of squander♫

16:48.090 --> 16:50.220
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

16:51.770 --> 16:54.010
♫When you're not here♫

16:54.530 --> 16:57.850
♫Life becomes aimless♫

16:58.710 --> 17:00.460
♫I miss you♫

17:01.470 --> 17:03.690
♫It's so real♫

17:04.710 --> 17:06.250
♫The person I trust♫

17:06.829 --> 17:07.930
♫Insists on separating♫

17:08.450 --> 17:11.480
♫Who can explain?♫

17:12.599 --> 17:14.730
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

17:15.569 --> 17:17.780
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

17:18.609 --> 17:21.400
♫To feel my heartache♫

17:22.020 --> 17:23.760
♫When I no longer have the best♫

17:24.650 --> 17:28.620
♫I miss you missing me♫

17:40.080 --> 17:41.720
♫When I walk the path you've walked♫

17:42.330 --> 17:45.390
♫Waiting to bump into you on the street♫

17:46.780 --> 17:48.430
♫Like yesterday♫

17:49.170 --> 17:51.820
♫Our forever had no end♫

17:52.970 --> 17:54.150
♫I'm the stupid one♫

17:56.750 --> 17:59.250
♫You've already engraved yourself in my pulse♫

18:00.690 --> 18:06.420
♫I don't want you to disappear like a rainbow♫

18:13.030 --> 18:13.850
Yan Yan.

18:14.180 --> 18:15.190
There's something I need

18:15.220 --> 18:16.460
to be honest with you about.

18:17.030 --> 18:19.390
Dazhong asked Jiang Chengyi as his best man.

18:19.550 --> 18:20.300
I thought Jiang Chengyi

18:20.350 --> 18:21.590
wouldn't have time to come.

18:21.740 --> 18:23.300
I didn't expect him to actually agree.

18:23.420 --> 18:24.350
So at the wedding,

18:24.390 --> 18:25.710
you'll definitely bump into him.

18:25.790 --> 18:26.780
Will you be okay?

18:29.790 --> 18:30.340
Yes.

18:30.400 --> 18:31.010
Okay.

18:31.110 --> 18:32.340
You're all busy.

18:32.460 --> 18:33.870
Just get here before the ceremony.

18:45.030 --> 18:47.070
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

18:46.070 --> 18:47.230
Move! Move!

18:47.510 --> 18:48.150
Doctor!

18:48.220 --> 18:48.860
Doctor!

18:49.260 --> 18:49.900
Help me.

18:51.030 --> 18:52.070
What are you doing?

18:52.460 --> 18:53.690
Who are you?

18:55.750 --> 18:56.880
Security!

18:56.940 --> 18:57.500
Security!

18:57.530 --> 18:58.340
There's someone here...

18:58.510 --> 18:59.160
What's wrong?

18:59.980 --> 19:00.640
What's wrong with you?

19:00.780 --> 19:01.440
Are you okay?

19:02.060 --> 19:02.630
Mom.

19:03.070 --> 19:03.760
I'm back.

19:03.990 --> 19:04.890
I'm at the door.

19:05.240 --> 19:06.700
The first shop was closed just now.

19:07.630 --> 19:08.070
Yes.

19:09.800 --> 19:10.590
I'll be right up.

19:10.590 --> 19:11.530
I'll hang up now.

19:12.490 --> 19:13.540
How are you feeling?

19:15.080 --> 19:15.910
Say something.

19:15.980 --> 19:16.990
It hurts.

19:17.270 --> 19:17.980
Nurse!

19:18.060 --> 19:18.430
Nurse!

19:18.450 --> 19:18.870
Hurry!

19:21.740 --> 19:22.420
Are you okay?

19:22.440 --> 19:24.120
W-What happened?

19:24.170 --> 19:25.100
He rushed up to me

19:25.150 --> 19:25.820
in a trance.

19:25.840 --> 19:27.050
Look, I'm now covered in blood.

19:27.100 --> 19:27.990
Look at me.

19:28.760 --> 19:29.730
What's wrong, young man?

19:30.230 --> 19:31.680
My stomach hurts.

19:31.790 --> 19:32.370
Where?

19:32.470 --> 19:33.090
My stomach hurts.

19:33.220 --> 19:33.900
My stomach hurts.

19:34.020 --> 19:34.950
Your stomach hurts?

19:42.650 --> 19:43.850
I'm from Xincheng Police.

19:43.870 --> 19:45.050
Please cooperate,

19:45.180 --> 19:46.490
and help me disperse the crowd.

19:46.740 --> 19:47.450
Okay.

19:48.030 --> 19:48.790
Stop looking here.

19:48.820 --> 19:49.700
Hurry up and go.

19:50.060 --> 19:50.780
Go out.

19:52.610 --> 19:53.330
Hurry up.

19:53.750 --> 19:54.980
Okay, let's go.

19:55.300 --> 19:55.830
Let's go.

20:20.860 --> 20:21.680
Nurse!

20:22.220 --> 20:24.400
Inform the director,

20:24.430 --> 20:25.100
and ask him to

20:25.100 --> 20:25.740
send some doctors here.

20:25.760 --> 20:26.140
Okay.

20:26.140 --> 20:26.540
Be quick.

20:33.520 --> 20:35.150
I am Jiang Chengyi from the Criminal Investigation Unit of

20:35.180 --> 20:35.820
Jinzhou, Xincheng.

20:36.700 --> 20:38.200
My police number is 135089.

20:38.450 --> 20:40.760
Currently, at Anshan People's Hospital,

20:40.870 --> 20:42.000
there's a patient

20:42.090 --> 20:43.280
with a bomb strapped on his abdomen.

20:43.650 --> 20:44.840
There's a trigger mechanism.

20:45.180 --> 20:46.450
I am not sure of the details yet.

20:46.470 --> 20:47.410
Send some people here immediately.

21:01.100 --> 21:03.910
[Police Coordination System]

21:01.260 --> 21:02.480
I want to see it live.

21:02.580 --> 21:03.030
Yes.

21:04.070 --> 21:04.630
Notify

21:04.750 --> 21:06.100
all police forces in the vicinity of the hospital

21:06.120 --> 21:06.960
to back up immediately.

21:06.990 --> 21:07.740
Evacuate the crowd

21:07.820 --> 21:08.460
and ensure safety.

21:08.550 --> 21:09.160
Yes.

21:19.960 --> 21:20.570
What happened?

21:20.590 --> 21:21.470
Why are they all outside?

21:21.600 --> 21:22.570
Dr. Huang.

21:22.740 --> 21:24.280
There's a special situation here.

21:24.310 --> 21:25.660
We need to evacuate immediately.

21:26.190 --> 21:26.710
What happened?

21:26.740 --> 21:27.100
What's wrong?

21:27.100 --> 21:28.420
We need to evacuate immediately.

21:28.360 --> 21:30.030
[Information Desk]

21:28.830 --> 21:30.200
Over there! You can't come in!

21:32.130 --> 21:33.020
Jiang!

21:34.600 --> 21:35.420
Dr. Han.

21:35.490 --> 21:36.230
This patient

21:36.230 --> 21:37.550
has a bomb tied to his abdomen.

21:37.820 --> 21:39.950
He just vomited and his stomach is aching.

21:40.070 --> 21:41.870
Currently, his limbs are cold,

21:41.890 --> 21:42.930
and his pulse is slow.

21:43.330 --> 21:45.360
There are many superficial wounds on his body.

21:45.860 --> 21:48.310
There is a possibility of active intra-abdominal bleeding

21:48.380 --> 21:49.740
and visceral rupture.

21:50.230 --> 21:51.030
Prepare for

21:51.060 --> 21:52.190
an X-ray immediately.

21:52.680 --> 21:53.270
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

21:53.590 --> 21:54.700
[Public Security]

21:54.700 --> 21:56.810
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

21:58.190 --> 21:59.310
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

22:08.930 --> 22:11.240
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital] [Traffic control in progress] [SWAT Team]

22:11.480 --> 22:12.780
Connect me to Jiang Chengyi.

22:12.820 --> 22:13.460
Yes.

22:16.810 --> 22:17.650
Comrade Chengyi,

22:18.070 --> 22:18.990
I'm Xing Feng.

22:19.110 --> 22:19.820
Director Xing.

22:20.870 --> 22:21.910
What's happening at the scene?

22:21.990 --> 22:22.780
Currently,

22:22.930 --> 22:24.030
the timer of the bomb shows

22:24.030 --> 22:25.400
we've about 12 minutes left.

22:25.710 --> 22:26.990
Based on my observation,

22:27.190 --> 22:27.950
this bomb

22:28.540 --> 22:29.420
not only has detonating wires,

22:29.920 --> 22:31.050
but also a trigger mechanism.

22:31.260 --> 22:32.910
[Selfless Service, Benevolent Heart and Expert Care]

22:32.090 --> 22:32.880
Dr. Han.

22:33.340 --> 22:34.590
How is the patient?

22:34.840 --> 22:37.380
He's in hypovolemia shock.

22:37.550 --> 22:39.310
We suspect a ruptured spleen in the abdominal cavity.

22:39.440 --> 22:40.410
If we don't

22:40.600 --> 22:41.950
operate on him now,

22:42.530 --> 22:44.000
his life will be in danger.

22:44.670 --> 22:45.580
How long more for

22:45.830 --> 22:46.840
the bomb squad to reach?

22:47.220 --> 22:48.730
Eight minutes, Sir!

22:48.820 --> 22:50.230
The traffic police has cleared

22:50.230 --> 22:50.950
all the roads for us.

22:52.220 --> 22:52.830
Commissioner Liu.

22:53.590 --> 22:54.190
Director Wang.

22:54.470 --> 22:56.090
I would like to apply for exceptional handling.

22:57.860 --> 22:58.450
Approved.

23:00.800 --> 23:01.580
Jiang Chengyi.

23:01.670 --> 23:02.130
Yes.

23:02.160 --> 23:03.050
You've worked in the

23:03.740 --> 23:05.100
bomb squad before, haven't you?

23:05.710 --> 23:06.130
Yes.

23:06.160 --> 23:07.530
I worked there for a year.

23:07.860 --> 23:08.470
Okay.

23:08.490 --> 23:09.770
This is an emergency.

23:10.220 --> 23:11.190
I order you

23:11.340 --> 23:12.380
to work with the doctors

23:12.420 --> 23:13.420
to dismantle the bomb,

23:13.450 --> 23:14.450
so as to deal with crisis on-site.

23:15.030 --> 23:16.320
I'll ask the bomb disposal experts

23:15.610 --> 23:19.420
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital] [Traffic control in progress] [SWAT Team]

23:16.460 --> 23:18.260
to guide you on the line.

23:18.630 --> 23:19.340
Are you confident?

23:19.830 --> 23:20.260
Yes.

23:20.580 --> 23:21.650
Comrade Jiang Chengyi.

23:21.700 --> 23:23.160
the interests of the people are paramount.

23:23.290 --> 23:25.710
We must do everything we can to ensure the safety of our people and property.

23:23.350 --> 23:27.240
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital] [Traffic control in progress] [SWAT Team]

23:25.790 --> 23:26.940
The bomb needs to be dismantled,

23:26.960 --> 23:27.470
and our people

23:28.810 --> 23:29.530
also needs saving.

23:29.700 --> 23:30.390
Roger.

23:29.780 --> 23:37.710
[Selfless Service, Benevolent Heart and Expert Care]

23:33.470 --> 23:34.190
Dr. Han.

23:34.390 --> 23:35.070
Time is limited.

23:35.580 --> 23:36.260
I now need to

23:36.290 --> 23:37.790
dismantle the bomb

23:37.810 --> 23:38.830
while you're treating the patient.

23:39.630 --> 23:40.440
Also,

23:40.800 --> 23:42.770
keep the operation's manpower to a minimum.

23:43.200 --> 23:43.840
Got it.

23:45.190 --> 23:46.680
Inform the anesthesiology and general surgery departments

23:46.770 --> 23:47.700
to get ready for the surgery immediately.

23:48.620 --> 23:49.330
Roger.

23:52.760 --> 23:53.510
Now,

23:54.270 --> 23:55.540
I need

23:55.900 --> 23:57.110
an anesthesiologist

23:57.580 --> 23:58.700
to complete the surgery with me.

23:59.060 --> 24:00.370
Who here is willing to go to the frontline?

24:01.190 --> 24:02.020
Director.

24:02.040 --> 24:02.770
I am.

24:03.300 --> 24:03.980
I’ll come.

24:06.390 --> 24:06.950
Dr. Han.

24:08.410 --> 24:09.490
I'm on duty today.

24:10.140 --> 24:11.000
Let me.

24:12.710 --> 24:13.430
Come with me.

24:35.330 --> 24:35.950
Connect for me.

24:35.970 --> 24:37.580
The operating room at Anshan District's Renmin Hospital.

24:38.070 --> 24:38.620
Yes.

24:39.640 --> 24:41.630
[Police]

24:41.690 --> 24:45.360
[Operating Room 01]

25:38.590 --> 25:40.300
[Operating Room 01]

25:39.220 --> 25:40.010
Jiang Chengyi.

25:40.250 --> 25:41.060
Is there any signal receiver

25:41.060 --> 25:42.190
on the relay?

25:45.070 --> 25:45.760
No.

25:46.340 --> 25:46.900
Okay.

25:47.390 --> 25:48.310
We can rule out

25:48.200 --> 25:54.450
[Operating Room 01]

25:48.340 --> 25:49.700
the possibility of a remote detonation.

26:11.120 --> 26:12.080
The spleen is cleaned.

26:11.230 --> 26:13.210
[Operating Room 01]

26:12.380 --> 26:13.580
The bleeding has stopped.

26:14.120 --> 26:14.790
Dr. Han.

26:15.670 --> 26:16.520
Leave the rest to me.

26:16.540 --> 26:17.330
Get out quickly.

26:17.420 --> 26:18.150
It's too dangerous.

26:18.620 --> 26:19.440
Be careful.

26:26.900 --> 26:27.810
I can't go.

26:28.680 --> 26:30.270
I need to monitor his blood pressure.

26:30.520 --> 26:31.460
If his blood pressure

26:31.460 --> 26:32.380
cannot be stabilized,

26:32.410 --> 26:33.730
the patient's life is in danger.

26:35.910 --> 26:37.170
The bomb could explode at any time.

26:37.200 --> 26:37.900
Are you sure?

26:37.950 --> 26:39.420
I'm his anesthesiologist.

26:39.590 --> 26:41.070
I cannot leave my patient.

26:44.080 --> 26:45.120
I'm going to dismantle the bomb now

26:45.610 --> 26:47.960
[Operating Room 01]

26:47.250 --> 26:48.260
SWAT team, firefighters,

26:48.710 --> 26:50.110
set up a bomb disposal area immediately.

26:50.360 --> 26:51.040
Members of the bomb squad,

26:51.790 --> 26:52.720
assist Jiang Chengyi.

26:53.370 --> 26:53.890
Yes.

26:54.390 --> 26:58.560
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

26:58.650 --> 27:01.230
[POLICE]

27:01.230 --> 27:01.650
[Ninghai Anshan People's Hospital]

27:01.920 --> 27:03.300
[POLICE]

27:09.090 --> 27:10.740
[Rehabilitation Department]

27:37.030 --> 27:37.860
Jiang Chengyi.

27:38.520 --> 27:39.640
When you move the bomb,

27:39.680 --> 27:40.830
be extra careful with the trigger's switch.

27:40.860 --> 27:41.660
Keep pressing onto it.

27:41.980 --> 27:42.680
Otherwise,

27:42.860 --> 27:44.300
the bomb will explode immediately.

28:03.380 --> 28:08.560
[Operating Room 01]

28:03.750 --> 28:04.860
Wait, Jiang Chengyi.

28:04.950 --> 28:05.860
Don't move.

28:06.290 --> 28:07.260
Zoom in.

28:07.280 --> 28:07.630
Yes.

28:09.850 --> 28:10.890
I want to see

28:11.300 --> 28:13.230
the wiring of the bomb's fuse.

28:18.250 --> 28:18.850
No.

28:19.580 --> 28:20.960
This is an anti-stripping device.

28:21.290 --> 28:22.070
Jiang Chengyi.

28:22.720 --> 28:24.110
This bomb is weight-sensitive.

28:24.270 --> 28:25.680
If it is moved gain,

28:26.050 --> 28:27.250
the bomb will explode.

28:28.040 --> 28:29.500
The only way now

28:29.830 --> 28:31.730
is to cut off the power of the bomb.

28:33.940 --> 28:35.270
If we cut the power now,

28:35.860 --> 28:36.820
is there still enough time?

28:36.860 --> 28:38.010
We have no choice.

28:38.240 --> 28:39.240
In this timeframe,

28:39.380 --> 28:40.540
the probability of successfully cutting the wire

28:40.570 --> 28:41.720
is about fifty-fifty.

28:43.210 --> 28:44.290
Which wire should I cut?

28:48.870 --> 28:50.150
The yellow wire on the left.

28:52.040 --> 28:52.740
This one?

28:52.940 --> 28:53.500
Yes.

28:53.590 --> 28:55.350
And the third red wire on the right.

28:57.060 --> 28:57.710
This one?

28:59.700 --> 29:01.480
These two wires need to be cut at the same time.

29:03.060 --> 29:04.020
The time difference

29:04.060 --> 29:05.210
musn't exceed 0.5 seconds.

29:05.580 --> 29:06.250
Otherwise,

29:06.700 --> 29:08.100
the bomb will explode.

29:08.540 --> 29:09.170
Lu Yan.

29:09.550 --> 29:10.910
Get out. Go.

29:11.420 --> 29:12.290
I'll cut it for you.

29:17.030 --> 29:17.960
There's no time.

29:17.990 --> 29:19.460
You can't cut both wires on your own.

29:22.060 --> 29:22.980
Trust me.

29:27.430 --> 29:29.820
[Operating Room 01]

29:39.550 --> 29:40.420
I trust you.

29:48.110 --> 29:49.260
Listen to my command.

29:50.250 --> 29:51.150
I'll count to three.

29:52.630 --> 29:53.540
You'll cut this wire.

29:53.840 --> 29:54.890
Are you ready?

30:00.840 --> 30:03.210
[Operating Room 01]

30:11.990 --> 30:12.770
Three.

30:15.600 --> 30:16.390
Two.

30:19.230 --> 30:19.830
One.

30:31.040 --> 30:37.530
[POLICE]

30:57.000 --> 30:58.040
The bomb has been dismantled.

30:58.730 --> 30:59.650
Prepare for detonation.

31:07.400 --> 31:08.270
Thank you.

31:18.200 --> 31:19.660
We'll take care of the rest.

31:44.840 --> 31:46.950
[Operation in Progress]

31:49.280 --> 31:50.790
The bleeding has been stopped.

31:51.690 --> 31:52.880
We are ready to close the abdomen.

31:53.230 --> 31:53.900
Lu Yan.

31:54.060 --> 31:55.170
Is the patient stable?

31:55.200 --> 31:56.300
All indicators are stable.

31:56.330 --> 31:57.020
I suggest to intubate

31:57.020 --> 31:57.790
and move the patient to the ICU.

31:58.250 --> 31:58.840
Okay.

31:59.620 --> 32:00.680
After the surgery,

32:00.710 --> 32:02.040
we've still got many hurdles to overcome.

32:17.810 --> 32:20.570
[Information Desk]

32:22.390 --> 32:23.140
Attention, please.

32:23.260 --> 32:24.490
The crisis has been resolved.

32:24.620 --> 32:26.260
Please evacuate in an orderly manner.

32:26.700 --> 32:27.520
Attention, please.

32:27.630 --> 32:28.900
The crisis has been resolved.

32:29.150 --> 32:30.630
Please evacuate in an orderly manner.

32:55.890 --> 32:58.770
[North Gate]

33:05.240 --> 33:08.030
[Rehabilitation Department]

33:10.480 --> 33:14.960
[Rehabilitation Department]

33:20.670 --> 33:21.520
Looking for me?

33:30.290 --> 33:33.690
[Rehabilitation Department]
